{"tid":1566261,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"深紅父母真係好撚煩","createTime":"2019-09-13T13:21:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T04:47:18.000Z","uid":319858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"b80ca5d60b9849b2618f49a561997fe8f1cdff26","tid":1566261,"uid":319858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:21:41.000Z","msg":"啱啱老豆見到阿妹書包上面條白絲帶<br />\n<br />\n之後就鬧話做咩掛呢D野 然後又好嬲<br />\n<br />\n阿妹咁啱去左街 之後老豆就走去拆左佢<br />\n<br />\n平時又話咩為左安全唔比參加之前遊行同阿妹鬧交<br />\n<br />\n搞到阿妹喊 我同佢地嘈過幾次都知道D低能深紅係最強的拒絕型<br />\n<br />\n講咩到最後都係浪費氣力<br />\n<br />\n呢次唔係參加遊行結果都係走去搞人地D野<br />\n<br />\n我又再一次基於呢D原則問題上覺得自己好廢<br />\n<br />\n無去幫阿妹保住條白絲帶 <br />\n<br />\n不過呢D象徵野我估拆左都無所謂<br />\n<br />\n最緊要都係個心<br />\n<br />\n啱啱好佢地訓身買左層千萬蚊ge樓<br />\n<br />\n一齊為香港攬炒出一分力<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/angel.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cab50b96369f06b0d4f23b3a41632f0920edc113","tid":1566261,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:22:15.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"84614c861593bb961fa45cc16061a6a8217f5c05","tid":1566261,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:22:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">9.15見！</span></span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SdUZfzj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSdUZfzj.jpg&h=0608c3e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kEm8TnK.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkEm8TnK.jpg&h=420447a4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"1445647f7f1eeb5d0a8e4a3c2a2f3d12a0184a97","tid":1566261,"uid":123713,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-13T13:22:40.000Z","msg":"[國際戰線] 香港人唔可以當其他國家係Condom!<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1565130\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1565130</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/thrHTWT.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FthrHTWT.jpg&h=21d791c5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"03320273cf7594ec5d0e3b257fa9fa7e8fb72b7c","tid":1566261,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:39:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"32a739e9b6b488b85bf9e26c1f365228907bfb91","tid":1566261,"uid":114766,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:39:39.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>其實你地知唔知