小學重演，唔駛好耐就會到其他界別。"},{"pid":"c624da632f792dd49d3e6418d7a0e438c0674c57","tid":1566261,"uid":77685,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T04:47:18.000Z","msg":"生左兩件垃圾"}]}